      "status": "candidate-context",
      "text": "Draw pretty micro benchmarking charts in HTML and allow to export them as png for benchee"
    },
    {
      "source_kind": "source-snippet",
      "source_repo": "bencheeorg/benchee_html",
      "status": "candidate-context",
      "text": "Formatter for [benchee](//github.com/PragTob/benchee) to produce some standalone HTML with nice graphs, a data table etc. from your benchee benchmarking results :) Also allows you to export PNG images, the graphs are also somewhat explorable thanks to [plotly.js](https://plot.ly\u2026"
    }
  ],
